take a cut
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[stock management] to move into a mob of stock and take out particular animals.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
